Good news , too , for those who want to spend their holiday under canvas : French Polynesia has a smattering of camping options . Do n't expect full-blown camp sites , though ; generally it 's a matter of guesthouses having areas where you can pitch your tent and have use of the facilities . The price ? Around US$ 15 per person .

